		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Add scale 2x, 3x, 4x.
<br />You can switch between them with the keys 1 to 5.
<br />1 = 1x
<br />2 = 2x
<br />3 = 3x
<br />4 = 4x
<br />5 = scale2x

		

		</td>
