	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I rewrote the entire graphics routines and have implemented fullscreen (no stretch for now) and added  the NTSC filter of blargg (many thx blargg, really good work). the keys are:
<br />1 = 1x
<br />2 = 2x
<br />3 = 3x
<br />4 = 4x
<br />5 = no filters
<br />6 = scale2x
<br />7 = ntsc
<br />, and . = choos type of ntsc filter (composite, svideo, rgc, monochrome)
<br />f = toggle fullscreen
<br />Link on first post are updated.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


