<br />Yeah it's supposed to be a secret message that's visible when zapper is pointed at the scroller or something like that. I haven't been able to test this on the real NES as I don't have a zapper but Bananmos should know how it *should* work. It somewhat works in Nintendulator when you attach the zapper to controller port #2. Doesn't seem to work at all in Nestopia...

		

